                                 B O O M F I E L D

BoomField is a new version of the game Minesweeper.
This game is Shareware. if you like the game, please send me $10 (USA).
You should copy the Libs and the Fonts to your sys:fonts and sys:libs in order to run 
BoomField.
If you don't know how to play, read the 'help' in the menu of the game.

Have fun!

           Alon Fliess.
 
